      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model selection and hemolysis damage model are justified for the flow regime and validated against relevant literature.",
      "rationale": "The SST k-omega turbulence model was selected based on its established performance for rotating internal flows at the relevant Reynolds numbers. The power-law hemolysis damage model (Giersiepen correlation) is the standard formulation used in FDA-cited literature. Model form is appropriate and justified."
